||'REVIEW'}</div><div style='font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px'>${c?.detail||'Pending assessment'}</div></div>`;}).join('')}</div></div><div class='section'><div class='section-title'>🔭 Threat Forecast</div><p style='font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px'><strong>Active Threat Actors:</strong> ${r.threat_actors_active||'None detected'}</p><div class='forecast-box'>${r.threat_forecast||'No forecast available'}</div></div><div class='footer'>🛡️ AEGIS ELITE v2.0 &nbsp;•&nbsp; Autonomous Enterprise & Guardian Intelligence System<br/>${init.report_id} &nbsp;•&nbsp; ${init.timestamp}<br/>All findings require verification by qualified security personnel. This report is confidential.</div></div></body></html>`;

